---

<footer class="footer-icons">
  <div class="icon-list">
    <span>Únete a las redes de la comunidad:</span>
    <a href="https://twitter.com/braulioucpech" target="_blank"><i class="nes-icon twitter is-medium"></i></a>
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/braulioup_/" target="_blank"><i class="nes-icon instagram is-medium"></i></a>
    <a href="https://github.com/BraulioUcPech" target="_blank"><i class="nes-icon github is-medium"></i></a>
